ve the perfect solution for you&#8230;<\/p>\n<h4>A step-by-step guide for getting started with succulents!<\/h4>\n<div id=\"attachment_7832\" style=\"width: 595px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7832\" class=\"wp-image-7832\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/08\/Find-out-how-to-water-what-soil-you-need-and-how-to-get-started-with-succulents.jpg\" alt=\"Find out how to water, what soil you need and how to get started with succulents!\" width=\"585\" height=\"877\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/08\/Find-out-how-to-water-what-soil-you-need-and-how-to-get-started-with-succulents-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/08\/Find-out-how-to-water-what-soil-you-need-and-how-to-get-started-with-succulents.jpg 667w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-7832\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><a href=\"https:\/\/leafandclay.co\/products\/echeveria-morning-beauty?variant=14732203459?rfsn=376597.71f09&subid=starterkit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow sponsored\">Echeveria subsessilis<\/a><\/p><\/div>\n<p>It's often hard to tell what is most important when caring for succulents because so much of it overlaps. So, let me walk you through how to start.<\/p>\n<h3>Buying Succulents<\/h3>\n<p>First, you'll need to get a succulent. Pretty obvious, right? If you're growing indoors, check out this list of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/top-10-indoor-succulents-and-more\/\">10 succulents I recommend for indoor growing<\/a>. If you're growing succulents outside in pots, check out this list of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/10-easy-to-grow-succulents-free-pdf\/\">10 easy to grow succulents<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h3>Pottery<\/h3>\n<p>Next, you'll need a pot for your succulent. One of the most important things when you're starting out with succulents is to use a pot with a drainage hole. This will make your succulent growing experience so much easier! There's a few other things to consider too, so take a look at my guide for <a href=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/choosing-the-right-pot-for-your-succulents\/\">choosing pottery for succulents<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h3>Soil<\/h3>\n<p>Now you'll want to get some well draining soil to plant your succulent in. One of the biggest mistakes I see people make is using regular potting soil for their succulents. Succulents need their roots to dry quickly and regular potting soil stays wet too long. See what makes a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/well-draining-soil-for-succulent-container-gardens\/\">good soil for succulents in this post<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h3>Planting<\/h3>\n<p>Once you have a succulent, pot and soil, it's time to start planting! Follow these step by step instructions for potting succulents and you'll be off to a good start. If you want a few more tips, you'll love <a href=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/tips-for-planting-succulents-in-containers\/\">this post<\/a>.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_5933\" style=\"width: 595px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5933\" class=\"wp-image-5933\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/05\/It-doesnt-take-much-to-get-started-with-planting-succuletns.jpg\" alt=\"It doesn't take much to get started with planting succulents!\" width=\"585\" height=\"877\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/05\/It-doesnt-take-much-to-get-started-with-planting-succuletns-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/05\/It-doesnt-take-much-to-get-started-with-planting-succuletns-700x1050.jpg 700w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/05\/It-doesnt-take-much-to-get-started-with-planting-succuletns.jpg 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-5933\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><a href=\"https:\/\/mountaincrestgardens.com\/crassula-ovata-gollum-jade\/?aff=2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored\">Crassula ovata &#8216;Gollum'<\/a><\/p><\/div>\n<h3>Watering<\/h3>\n<p>An now, the ultimate piece of advice for growing succulents&#8230; how to water! If you've followed the advice above, watering your succulents will be a cinch with the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/how-to-water-succulent-plants\/\">soak and dry method<\/a>. See exactly what the soak and dry method is and how to properly water succulents in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/how-to-water-succulent-plants\/\">this post<\/a>.<\/p>\n<h4>And that's it!<\/h4>\n<p>If you follow those basic instructions you'll be on your way to growing beautiful, healthy succulents.<\/p>\n<p>Now, if you'd rather not go to the hassle of finding succulents, a pot, and well draining soil, and if you'd like a reference guide by your side while you're potting&#8230;\u00a0or if you want a simple gift for a friend,\u00a0I have a great option\u00a0for you&#8230;<\/p>\n<h3>A succulent starter kit!<\/h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_7831\" style=\"width: 595px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-7831\" class=\"wp-image-7831\" src=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/08\/This-succulent-starter-kit-is-a-great-gift-for-college-students.jpg\" alt=\"This succulent starter kit is a great gift for college students!\" width=\"585\" height=\"877\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/08\/This-succulent-starter-kit-is-a-great-gift-for-college-students-500x750.jpg 500w, https:\/\/www.succulentsandsunshine.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/08\/This-succulent-starter-kit-is-a-great-gift-for-college-students.jpg 667w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-7831\" cl